	----- Original Message -----
	From: Don Benjamin <Don.Benjamin@nerc.net>
	To: Operating Committee <oc@nerc.com>
	Cc: Regional Managers <managers@nerc.com>
	Sent: Monday, April 30, 2001 2:24 PM
	Subject: Ballot for Control Area Criteria v2 and Policy 3 v4


	Dear Operating Committee:

	To date, we have received no comments on either the Control Area
	Criteria or Policy 3.  I need your ballot on these two documents by
the
	end of the day on May 4.  If they pass by 2/3 affirmative vote, then
	I'll send on to the Board for approval in June.

	Both docs are attached.

	I've also attached a spiffy little ballot for you to use.  Just
enter
	your name and click on the Yes or No boxes, and then send it to me
as an
	e-mail attachment.  Remember to press your mouse button hard -- I
don't
	what to have to deal with hanging chads.  The ballot is "dumb" and
you
	can press both yes and no for the same item, so just don't do that
or
	I'll have to call you.

	If you don't want to mess with this form, just drop me an e-mail.

	thanks,

	don.






